    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瓦尔索斯召唤你加入他的阵营。在这款扣人心弦的动作角色扮演游戏中，与成群的怪物和亡灵生物战斗，它们只有一个目标：杀死你。化身阵亡英雄，投入战斗——如果你失败了，瓦尔索斯将为你唤醒下一位战士。死亡只是开始：死亡，重生，并从前辈的经验和成就中获益。战斗，死亡，重复——争夺世界王位的战斗已经打响。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特色：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 扣人心弦的动作角色扮演游戏，融合了砍杀和 Rogue-lite 元素</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 单人和多人模式，最多可容纳 3 名玩家</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 直接控制英雄，可升级，无需固定职业</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 随机生成的地下城</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065870/extras/8dba649ceb6d9b32438c6be7f160760a.poster.avif?t=1771342052\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065870/extras/8dba649ceb6d9b32438c6be7f160760a.webm?t=1771342052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065870/extras/8dba649ceb6d9b32438c6be7f160760a.mp4?t=1771342052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Rogue-lite 单人及多人游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单人或与好友联手：对抗邪恶势力，并在团战中巧妙运用你的技能。在多人游戏中与队友交换物品，增强团队战斗力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065870/extras/b65b3e845d059c013de74d1a73915967.poster.avif?t=1771342052\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065870/extras/b65b3e845d059c013de74d1a73915967.webm?t=1771342052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065870/extras/b65b3e845d059c013de74d1a73915967.mp4?t=1771342052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>独特的角色发展</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“你穿什么就是什么”——没有预设的英雄职业，你可以完全自由地选择装备和角色扮演方式。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065870/extras/511ec59aa5d2c0e523ec527426d712e0.poster.avif?t=1771342052\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065870/extras/511ec59aa5d2c0e523ec527426d712e0.webm?t=1771342052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065870/extras/511ec59aa5d2c0e523ec527426d712e0.mp4?t=1771342052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>丰富的游戏世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索拥有开阔景观和地下城的不同区域。这些区域会在你每次开始新游戏时随机生成。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065870/extras/1b9a1b9c6131593fbe903ec42ffad431.poster.avif?t=1771342052\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065870/extras/1b9a1b9c6131593fbe903ec42ffad431.webm?t=1771342052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065870/extras/1b9a1b9c6131593fbe903ec42ffad431.mp4?t=1771342052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>直接控制</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直接控制你的英雄：我们不再使用点击操作来移动角色，而是依靠 WASD 键进行移动，并使用鼠标进行精确瞄准。</p>",
